title: Finally, The Final Podcast on the World Cup Final
description: Cat and Dan are back to cover the highlights from the last week of cricket. Topics include: The World Cup Final (featuring Marnus's thoughts) Australia's shameful T20 series loss against India Are You Smarter Than A Fifth Grade Cricketer?
